  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nSpecifically crafted HTML file can trigger Use After Free of Device object in GPU process. This bug can potentially be exploited to achieve one click Remote Code Execution in a privileged process (i.e. the GPU process), or be exploited to escape sandbox from a compromise"
